Hackathon project:

Nearby holiday finder:
   A predefined set of departure ufis in a drop down (10 big cities in Europe from bookers)
       For each of these, come up with all possible names (and countries) for Transaction.booker_city.
   A maximum radius (or unlimited).
   Number of day into the past to search (or hardcode to 3 days).
   Checkin-checkout dates for availability checks.
Output:
   A list of cities, with visitor counts and clickable links to Booking.com (with check-in/out dates).


