Dear Toastmasters Amsterdam,

I am interested in improving my public speaking skills, and found about your group on the Toastmasters website. I am a software developer, born and educated in Mexico, working for the travel company Booking.com. I am 41 years old, married, with two children. My home town is Monterrey, but I have lived in many places: Gudalajara, Mexico City, Cuernavaca and Chiapas in Mexico; Palo Alto and San Francisco in the US, and here in Amsterdam since five years ago. I went to college at ITESM in Monterrey and Stanford University in California. 

