    1. add "add youtube video" link. 
    2. When clicked, card becomes wider, a text area appears for the link.
    3. When the link is submitted, it gets parsed, the video id extracted (http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lddUnv1R5y0), and the video thumbnail image is shown (clickable, with a white triangle that changes color in the middle).
    4. When the link is clicked, display video in nyromodal popup, as above.
    5. That's it!!!

