==================================================
==== AntTrade, marketing message
==================================================

USER INTERFACE / MARKETING MSG

Make someone happy. Bring them something from home.

How this works:

Chuma lives in Amsterdam, but grew up in Egypt. He misses sesame paste from home. 

He logs in to AntTrade and requests any traveler coming from Egypt to Amsterdam to bring him two jars of his favorite brand sesame paste.  (http://imgs.tootoo.com/b8/6e/b86e15b2293ad71728fdcd2fc75f2e94.jpg)

In return, he offers to pay for the cost of the paste, and a boxed gift of Dutch chocolates.

Darius lives in Egypt. He travels frequently to Amsterdam on business. He logs in to AntTrade and offers to carry Chuma's sesame paste along in his next trip. They arrange that Chuma will pick up the paste at Darius' hotel in one evening of his stay.

Chuma gets his yummy sesame paste. Darius is happy to help and receives a box of chocolates to take home!

The world is a better place. [Smiling world image]


On the left:
    ----
If you travel:

1. Check if someone in your destination wants something from your location.
2. Offer to bring what they want!

[Start here!]

    ----

If you live far away from home:

1. Enter your location, what you want and what city or country it can be brought from.

2. Enter what you can give in return for the favor.

[Start here!]


==================================================
==== UI
==================================================
  
I am traveling and can bring stuff along for others.

  ==> Where do you depart from? (Airport code / Country - Province/State - City)

(get from http://www.maxmind.com/app/worldcities)

 Select Country (doable)
 Load / Select State (sub-country region)
 Select City

  ==> Where are you traveling to? (one or more destinations) 

 Select Country (doable)
 Load / Select State (sub-country region)
 Select City [Add]

Selecting a country loads state (if state available in Db)
Selecting a state loads cities
Selecting a city and clicking add adds the city into a list.

[AQUI VOY]

I want someone to bring something for me.



AntTrade

A website to:

Have people request travelers to bring them stuff from their places of origin.

UI:

For people who need stuff, a way to express the need:

   From (country - city - region), please bring me (this and that).

   I will pay the value of the merchandise (in Euro) and also (X euro/USD/etc) comission for bringing it.

   (an expiry date)

Also, to contact travelers who have stated they're going somewhere and ask them to bring something for them.


For travelers:

A form to enter where they're departing from and where they're going to, to state that they're available to bring something along.

Also, search for recipients in the city they're going to, and offer to bring their stuff to them.


