1. define templates

2. make a script to extract TMPL_VAR texts into a translation targets table. The script will extract all vars, except those that are real program variables, which will start with a certain prefix, such as "b_".

   Every time new texts are added to a template, this script can be run to make the new texts available for translation.
 
3. Make a tool to allow users to populate the Translations table.

4. When displaying the website, retrieve translations on the fly from the database, only the ones needed for the page being retrieved.

5. Merge translations and template, and voila!

